item.title: GSB 570 PROFESSIONAL (IMPACT DRILL)
item.dc:creator: lekhitanand456
item.description: Accessible Bosch quality: upgrade your no-name tool to a branded tool from Bosch without breaking the wallet Performance: powerful 570 Watt motor enables you to drill holes up to Ø10 mm in steel and Ø13 mm in masonry with ease Enhanced durability: reliable and accessible impact drill with durable metal chuck
item.content:encoded: Powerful and reliable power tool.

item.title: Electric Drilling Machine
item.dc:creator: lekhitanand456
item.description: Cordless Drilling Machine，12V Drill Driver with w/Li-ion Battery/Charger，For Torpedo Level, Wire Pliers for Wood, Furniture Installation
item.content:encoded:
• Rubber-covered handle with ergonomic design provides maximum comfort grip for being breezily operated in one hand and less vibration，Not easy to fall off,minimizes fatigue in most daily jobs.
  • 【3/8 Keyless Chuck & Forward/Reserve Control】Working with LIKI impact drill set makes everything easier than before, which is a powerful all-around helper for matching your desires, perfect for professional and DIYers! 3/8’’ keyless chuck provides an automatic spindle lock that enables one-hand changing with great accessory compatibility. The Forward/Reverse switch allows you to either screw or replaces/remove bits for your purposes. Built-in a strong magnet that can hold the bits anytime.
